explanation.summary: Kt qu in tim cho thy nhp tim ca bn chm hn mc bnh thng, nhng cc tn hiu in khc trong tim vn n nh.
explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy nhp tim u v cc sng in tim (P, QRS, T) c hnh dng bnh thng, nhng khong cch gia cc nhp di hn so vi ngi khe mnh. C th, nhp tim ca bn l 54.12 ln/pht, thp hn ngng bnh thng (60-100 ln/pht). Tuy nhin, thi gian dn truyn in qua cc bung tim chnh (QRS Duration l 0.111 giy) vn nm trong gii hn an ton, cho thy ng dn truyn in trong tim hot ng tt, khng c du hiu tc nghn.
explanation.recommendations: Nhp tim chm c th l bnh thng  mt s ngi, c bit l vn ng vin, hoc khi bn ang ng. Hy theo di c th v ghi nhn bt k triu chng no nh chng mt, mt mi bt thng, kh th hoc ngt xu.
explanation.next_steps: Nu bn khng c bt k triu chng no nu trn, bn c th tip tc theo di ti nh. Nu xut hin cc triu chng nh mt mi, chng mt thng xuyn, hoc cm thy tim p qu chm gy kh chu, hy n gp bc s tim mch  c kim tra k hn.
